      "rationale": "Validation metrics were computed per ASME V&V 20. For NIH, E% = 12.4% (acceptance ≤15%). For pressure head, E% = 4.8% (acceptance ≤10%). Experimental uncertainty was propagated from reported measurement uncertainties. Both metrics satisfy their acceptance criteria, supporting confidence in the model's predictive capability for the COU quantities of interest."
